headline: New Owner Takes Possession of Their Third PostalAnnex Store Located in San Jose, California--Offering Shipping and Office Services
summary: Annex Brands, Inc., a leading franchisor in the packing, shipping, and office services industries, is pleased to announce the successful transfer of ownership of an existing 34 year-old PostalAnnex location in San Jose, CA to new owners, Sanjay Gupta and Deepika Chopra. This transition to new ownership ensures that the community will benefit from the essential shipping and office services.
